    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>i made these and they are indeed the best chocolate chips cookies ever. i added walnuts and used fancy flake salt, which i think kind of made the whole thing. i did use the chocolate discs, as well, because they have them in bulk at the store by us, and i think they actually did make a difference. with the discs, the chocolate and dough make thin alternating layers throughout and i think make for better texture and more even distribution. that being said, you can&#8217;t go wrong with good ol&#8217; chocolate chips, either.</p>
