    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Here&#8217;s the thing I still don&#8217;t understand about using two flours.  Bread flour has a lot of protein; cake flour has very little protein.  If you use both flours, don&#8217;t they average out into the protein content of AP flour?  By the way, I so agree about eating chocolate chip cookies cold.  COLD, in my case.  We always keep them in the freezer.</p>
