      <p>i had both cake and bread flour, so used them as in original recipe.  used up lots of chocolate odds and ends (60% chips, 60% bar, semi-sweet chips).  added maybe a teaspoon of orange zest.  dough sat in fridge for 2 days before baking.  AMAZING!!!  and so easy when using a scale.  may add some toasted pecans or almonds next time &#8211; there will be many next times&#8230;.</p>
